{"tid":159491,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩納哥大將望出戰李城：我要幫雲尼亞里報仇！","createTime":"2017-03-17T04:56:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T05:50:12.000Z","uid":10199,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cec84d1d3359271003e8b11fa8493bea1ab6a2eb","tid":159491,"uid":10199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T04:56:07.000Z","msg":"無幾耐之前，歐聯8強既參賽隊伍，就已經塵埃落定啦，而祖雲達斯隊長保方，同埋皇家馬德里教練施丹都表示，唔希望喺8強度，迎戰來自英超既李斯特城，話狐狸軍團係一支好有鬥心既球隊喎。<br />\n<br />\n不過，摩納哥中堅拉治（Andrea Raggi）就表示，自己好想喺歐聯8強入面，出戰李斯特城，原因就係希望為前任狐狸軍團教練雲尼亞里報復！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n喺執教李斯特城之前，雲尼亞里就曾經喺摩納哥教過2季，而拉治當時就係雲帥既愛將之一，所以佢地其實都幾師徒情深架。拉治仲話，喺摩納哥將曼城踢出局之後，雲尼亞里都有send sms去祝賀佢地！睇黎雲帥既人事關係處理，都唔算太差姐。"},{"pid":"dbffa46f2bf1218ebd07a1315f31ab91b493b092","tid":159491,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T05:06:56.000Z","msg":"想抽李城搵藉口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"317451e37e8c22df4a49e0756a46efb0be8b74f9","tid":159491,"uid":34490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T05:08:35.000Z","msg":"係就好睇"},{"pid":"437d25d4b7f915100f012f6cbe8adbda8f6e0404","tid":159491,"uid":34513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T05:10:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係就好睇</blockquote><br />\n剩低個3場一定係大戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec1fe33687c5e93f51eebc34e64b9817d1f12243","tid":159491,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T05:15:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係就好睇</blockquote><br />\n剩低個3場一定係大戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n皇巴拜多祖馬互片"},{"pid":"f8adee381c2e3fe2ffb7e8483dc165ce26b4e415","tid":159491,"uid":4179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T05:45:20.000Z","msg":"曼聯幫摩佬報仇未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c88042500a002203ea87ef7a054908cadfbd547b","tid":159491,"uid":10338,"like":